### Fixture Match Timeline — HTTP cases (spec 0033)
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/api/v1

@base = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@admin_key = {{ADMIN_API_KEY}}

# ─── Backfill: ingestar eventos de un partido ya ingested ──────────────────
# Útil para partidos anteriores al deploy de 0033 o para re-procesar.
# Consume 1 request de API-Football quota.
# Sin admin key configurada, no requiere header (DEBUG mode).

### Backfill — fixture WC existente (Norway 4-2 Iraq)
POST {{base}}/admin/fixtures/1539016/ingest-events
X-Admin-Key: {{admin_key}}

### Backfill — otro partido de grupo (sin key en dev)
POST {{base}}/admin/fixtures/1489369/ingest-events

# ─── Detalle de partido con events ─────────────────────────────────────────
# GET /wc/fixtures/{fixture_external_id}
# El campo "events" es lista vacía si no hay datos backfilled.
# Orden: minute ASC, extra_minute ASC, source_sequence ASC NULLS LAST.

### Detail con events (fixture ya backfilled)
GET {{base}}/wc/fixtures/1539016

### Detail sin events (fixture futuro / no backfilled)
GET {{base}}/wc/fixtures/9999999

# ─── Verificar tabla desde psql ───────────────────────────────────────────
# docker compose exec db psql -U sfa -d sfa -c \
#   "SELECT fixture_external_id, event_type, minute, player_name
#    FROM fixture_events
#    WHERE fixture_external_id = 1539016
#    ORDER BY minute, extra_minute;"
